metadata.description: I GOT A FIRE IN MY BELLY, AND IT KEEPS ME CREATIVE. I DON'T LET MY SHADOWS GET ME DOWN, I BURN THROUGH THEM LIKE FLAMES. LOUD, HEAVY, HOT, PASSIONATE. This is an idea and I like it a lot. I hope you like it too. If you don't, there will be MANY, MANY MORE.
